Through the grace and compassions and love for mankind of Thine Only-begotten Son, with whom thou art blessed, together with thy most holy and good, and life-creating Spirit: now and ever, and unto the ages of ages.}{\fs32  
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0 {\fs20 People: Amen.}{\fs32  
