Then the priest boweth and likewise the deacon, on the place where he standeth, while saying secretly thrice:
\par }\pard\plain \s45\qj \li576\ri576\sb100\sa100\sl360\slmult1\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin576\lin576\itap0 \f1\fs36\cf15\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs43\b\i\fs28 Priest:}{ O God, cleanse me a sinner, and have mercy upon me. }{
\cs44\i\fs30\cf6 Thrice.}{\fs30  }{
\par }\pard\plain \s25\ql \li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin360\lin360\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 
And when the deacon seeth the priest stretch out his hands and touch the Holy Bread in order to make the holy elevation, he exclaimeth: 
