\par }\pard\plain \s19\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\keepn\nowidctlpar\faauto\outlinelevel2\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\fs36\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs40 \sect }\sectd \linex0\sectdefaultcl \pard\plain 
\s19\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\keepn\nowidctlpar\faauto\outlinelevel2\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\fs36\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs40 The Elevation
\par }\pard\plain \s25\ql \li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin360\lin360\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 And the priest, elevating the Holy Bread exclaimeth: 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Priest:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 Holy Things are for the Holy. 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0 {\fs20 People: One is Holy, One is Lord: Jesus Christ, to the glory of God the Father. Amen.}{\fs32  
\par }\pard\plain \s25\ql \li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin360\lin360\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 And the choir chanteth the communion verse of the day, or of the saint. 
